{
  "keyword": "RNMOBJ",
  "description": "Rename Object (RNMOBJ)",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "OBJ",
      "description": "Object",
      "help": "Object (OBJ)\n\nSpecifies the object to be renamed. If the library (qualifier 2) is not specified, *LIBL is used. A library name can be specified for qualifier 2 to ensure that the correct object is renamed.\n\nThis is a required parameter.\n\nQualifier 1: Object\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
